			description: [
				"&e&lSide Quest · Productive Bees.&r"
				""
				"A whole different way to automate: you don't build a machine, you breed a &olivestock&r that makes the resource for you."
				""
				"Bees live in hives, eat flowers, and their comb centrifuges into ingots, gems and dusts. Cross-breed two bees and you get a rarer one that makes rarer loot. It runs while you're off doing anything else."
				""
				"&7None of this is required to win. It's the slow, hands-off branch - set it up once and walk away.&r"
			]
