		{
			dependencies: ["0BEE000000000003"]
			description: [
				"Comb isn't the resource - it's the &opackaging&r. A &eCentrifuge&r spins comb into what's actually inside: iron, gold, redstone, whatever that breed produces."
				""
				"Hopper comb in, pull ingots out. The bee did the mining; the centrifuge does the smelting."
