				"The whole point of bees: &ecross-breeding&r. Put two bees in a &eBreeding Chamber&r and you get a chance at a new species that makes something rarer than either parent."
				""
				"This is the tech tree. Common bees breed toward diamond bees, then toward things you'd normally have to fight for."
